[
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "1. Find the value of ∫₀^π |sin 2x| dx", "c": "<strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Split the integral based on the sign of sin 2x<br><br>sin 2x ≥ 0 on [0, π/2] and sin 2x ≤ 0 on [π/2, π]<br><br>∫₀^π |sin 2x| dx = ∫₀^(π/2) sin 2x dx - ∫_(π/2)^π sin 2x dx<br><br>Step 2: Evaluate each integral<br><br>= [-½ cos 2x]₀^(π/2) - [-½ cos 2x]_(π/2)^π<br><br>= (-½(-1) - (-½(1))) - (-½(1) - (-½(-1)))<br><br>= (½ + ½) - (-½ - ½) = 1 - (-1) = 2<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 2</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "2. Find the volume of the solid generated by revolving the shaded region about the x-axis.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 180 300 L 240 0' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><polygon points='200,200 230,200 200,50' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='230' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>2</text><text x='175' y='55' fill='white' font-size='14'>10</text><text x='210' y='100' fill='white' font-size='14'>y + 5x = 10</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Express y in terms of x<br><br>y = 10 - 5x<br><br>Step 2: Set up the volume integral using the disc method<br><br>V = π ∫₀² y² dx = π ∫₀² (10 - 5x)² dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate the integral<br><br>Let u = 10 - 5x, then du = -5 dx<br><br>When x = 0, u = 10. When x = 2, u = 0<br><br>V = π ∫₁₀ u² (-1/5) du = (π/5) ∫₀¹⁰ u² du<br><br>V = (π/5)[u³/3]₀¹⁰ = (π/5)(1000/3) = 200π/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 200π/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "3. Find the shaded area of the following figure.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 180 100 Q 220 260 260 100' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 180 100 Q 220 260 260 100 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><line x1='150' y1='100' x2='290' y2='100' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='1'/><text x='295' y='105' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = 5</text><text x='225' y='50' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = (x - 1)² + 1</text><text x='205' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>0</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find the intersection points<br><br>(x - 1)² + 1 = 5<br>(x - 1)² = 4<br>x - 1 = ±2<br>x = -1, 3<br><br>Step 2: Set up the area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₋₁³ [5 - ((x - 1)² + 1)] dx<br>= ∫₋₁³ (4 - (x - 1)²) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate the integral<br><br>Let u = x - 1, then du = dx<br>Limits: [-1, 3] → [-2, 2]<br><br>Area = ∫₋₂² (4 - u²) du = [4u - u³/3]₋₂²<br>= (8 - 8/3) - (-8 + 8/3) = 16 - 16/3 = 32/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 32/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "4. Find the shaded area.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 160 120 Q 220 360 280 120' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 180 200 Q 220 360 260 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='170' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>-1</text><text x='265' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>3</text><text x='230' y='120' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x² - 2x - 3</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: The curve is below x-axis between x = -1 and x = 3<br><br>Step 2: Set up the area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₋₁³ -(x² - 2x - 3) dx = ∫₁³ (-x² + 2x + 3) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate the integral<br><br>= [-x³/3 + x² + 3x]₋₁³<br>= (-27/3 + 9 + 9) - (1/3 + 1 - 3)<br>= (-9 + 18) - (1/3 - 2) = 9 - (-5/3) = 9 + 5/3 = 32/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 32/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "5. Find the shaded area.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 170 200 L 270 0 M 150 150 Q 200 300 280 -60' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 180 180 Q 220 260 260 20 L 180 180' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='185' y='145' fill='white' font-size='14'>3</text><text x='250' y='180' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x²</text><text x='160' y='100' fill='white' font-size='14' transform='rotate(-60 160 100)'>y = 2x + 3</text><text x='185' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>O</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find intersection points<br><br>x² = 2x + 3<br>x² - 2x - 3 = 0<br>(x - 3)(x + 1) = 0<br>x = -1, 3<br><br>Step 2: Set up the area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₋₁³ (2x + 3 - x²) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate<br><br>= [x² + 3x - x³/3]₁³<br>= (9 + 9 - 9) - (1 - 3 + 1/3)<br>= 9 - (-5/3) = 9 + 5/3 = 32/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 32/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "6. Find the area of the shaded region.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 170 230 L 250 150 M 170 230 C 190 200, 200 185, 215 170 C 225 140, 230 100, 235 50' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 185 200 C 195 200, 200 185, 215 170 C 220 140, 225 100, 230 65 L 230 170 L 185 215 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='175' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>-1</text><text x='230' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>2</text><text x='255' y='155' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x</text><text x='235' y='55' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x³ + 1</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up the area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₋₁² (x² + 1 - x) dx<br><br>Step 2: Evaluate the integral<br><br>= [x³/3 + x - x²/2]₋₁²<br>= (8/3 + 2 - 2) - (-1/3 - 1 - 1/2)<br>= 8/3 - (-11/6) = 16/6 + 11/6 = 27/6 = 9/2<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 9/2</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "7. Find the shaded area.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 180 20 L 260 260' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><polygon points='200,200 240,200 200,80' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='185' y='85' fill='white' font-size='14'>2</text><text x='235' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>2/3</text><text x='185' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>O</text><text x='230' y='140' fill='white' font-size='14' transform='rotate(71.5 230 140)'>f(x)=-3x+2</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up the definite integral<br><br>Area = ∫₀^(2/3) (-3x + 2) dx<br><br>Step 2: Evaluate<br><br>= [-3x²/2 + 2x]₀^(2/3)<br>= (-3/2(4/9) + 2(2/3)) - 0<br>= -2/3 + 4/3 = 2/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 2/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "8. Find the area of the region bounded by the curve y = x³ - 4x² + 3x and the x-axis.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 180 250 C 200 120, 230 150, 240 200 C 260 330, 300 330, 320 200 C 330 130, 340 50, 350 0' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 200 200 C 210 160, 230 160, 240 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><path d='M 240 200 C 260 300, 300 300, 320 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='190' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>0</text><text x='260' y='100' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x³ - 4x² + 3x</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find x-intercepts<br><br>x³ - 4x² + 3x = 0<br>x(x² - 4x + 3) = 0<br>x(x - 1)(x - 3) = 0<br>x = 0, 1, 3<br><br>Step 2: Set up area integral<br><br>Area = ₀¹ (x³ - 4x² + 3x) dx + ∫₁³ -(x³ - 4x² + 3x) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate<br><br>(x³ - 4x² + 3x) dx = x⁴/4 - 4x³/3 + 3x²/2<br><br>For [0,1]: (1/4 - 4/3 + 3/2) = 5/12<br>For [1,3]: |(81/4 - 36 + 27/2) - 5/12| = 32/12<br><br>Total = 5/12 + 32/12 = 37/12<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 37/12</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "9. Find the area contained between the line y = 2x and the curve y = x²", "c": "<strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find intersection points<br><br>x² = 2x<br>x² - 2x = 0<br>x(x - 2) = 0<br>x = 0, 2<br><br>Step 2: Set up area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₀² (2x - x²) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate<br><br>= [x² - x³/3]₀² = (4 - 8/3) - 0 = 4/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 4/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "10. Find the volume of revolution formed when the curve f(x) = √(sin x) for 0 ≤ x ≤ π/2 is rotated through 360° about the x-axis", "c": "<strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up volume integral (disc method)<br><br>V = π ₀^(π/2) [f(x)]² dx = π ∫₀^(π/2) (√(sin x))² dx<br><br>Step 2: Simplify and evaluate<br><br>V = π ∫₀^(π/2) sin x dx = π[-cos x]₀^(π/2)<br>= π(-cos(π/2) + cos 0) = π(0 + 1) = π<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: π</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "11. Find the shaded area of the following figure.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 130 220 Q 200 -160 270 220' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 140 200 Q 200 -160 260 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='135' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>-3</text><text x='190' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>0</text><text x='255' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>3</text><text x='205' y='25' fill='white' font-size='14'>9</text><text x='240' y='80' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = 9 - x²</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up the area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₋³ (9 - x²) dx<br><br>Step 2: Evaluate<br><br>= [9x - x³/3]₋₃³<br>= (27 - 9) - (-27 + 9)<br>= 18 - (-18) = 36<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 36</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "12. The diagram shown part of the curve y = sin(2x + π/3). Find the area of the shaded region.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 170 113 C 200 -20, 250 100, 280 200' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 200 113 C 230 40, 260 100, 280 200 L 200 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='185' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>O</text><text x='260' y='225' fill='white' font-size='14'>(π/3, 0)</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up the integral<br><br>Area = ∫₀^(π/3) sin(2x + π/3) dx<br><br>Step 2: Evaluate<br><br>= [-½ cos(2x + π/3)]₀^(π/3)<br>= -½[cos(π) - cos(π/3)]<br>= -½[-1 - ½] = -½[-3/2] = 3/4<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 3/4</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "13. Find the shaded area.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 100 100 Q 250 400 400 -200 M 150 250 Q 300 -100 400 200' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 200 200 Q 250 250 300 100 Q 250 50 200 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='185' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>O</text><text x='270' y='80' fill='white' font-size='14'>y=x²</text><text x='310' y='160' fill='white' font-size='14'>y=2x-x²</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find intersection points<br><br>x² = 2x - x²<br>2x² - 2x = 0<br>2x(x - 1) = 0<br>x = 0, 1<br><br>Step 2: Set up area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₀¹ (2x - x² - x²) dx = ∫₀¹ (2x - 2x²) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate<br><br>= [x² - 2x³/3]₀¹ = (1 - 2/3) - 0 = 1/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 1/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "14. The shaded area is 12a unit². Find the exact value of a.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 120 -40 Q 200 260 280 -40' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 140 200 L 140 20 Q 200 260 260 20 L 260 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='130' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>-a</text><text x='190' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>O</text><text x='255' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>a</text><text x='230' y='60' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x² + 2</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up the integral<br><br>Area = ₋ₐᵃ (x² + 2) dx = [x³/3 + 2x]₋ₐ<br>= (a³/3 + 2a) - (-a³/3 - 2a) = 2a³/3 + 4a<br><br>Step 2: Equate to 12a<br><br>2a³/3 + 4a = 12a<br>2a³/3 = 8a<br>2a³ = 24a<br>a² = 12 (since a > 0)<br>a = √12 = 2√3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 2√3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "15. The shaded area is 6r unit². Find the value of r.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 120 20 Q 200 320 280 20' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 140 200 L 140 80 Q 200 320 260 80 L 260 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='130' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>-r</text><text x='190' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>0</text><text x='255' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>r</text><text x='250' y='40' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x²</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up the integral<br><br>Area = ∫₋ᵣʳ x² dx = [x³/3]₋ᵣʳ = r³/3 - (-r³/3) = 2r³/3<br><br>Step 2: Equate to 6r<br><br>2r³/3 = 6r<br>2r³ = 18r<br>r² = 9 (since r > 0)<br>r = 3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "16. Evaluate the integral ∫₀^(2/3) (-3x + 2) dx", "c": "<strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find antiderivative<br><br>∫(-3x + 2) dx = -3x²/2 + 2x<br><br>Step 2: Evaluate at limits<br><br>= [-3x²/2 + 2x]₀^(2/3)<br>= (-3/2(4/9) + 2(2/3)) - 0<br>= -2/3 + 4/3 = 2/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 2/3</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "17. Find the area contained between the line y = x and the curve y = x²", "c": "<strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find intersection points<br><br>x = x²<br>x² - x = 0<br>x(x - 1) = 0<br>x = 0, 1<br><br>Step 2: Set up area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₀¹ (x - x²) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate<br><br>= [x²/2 - x³/3]₀¹ = (1/2 - 1/3) - 0 = 1/6<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 1/6</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "18. Find the shaded area.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 140 185 L 260 42.5 M 155 65 Q 192.5 297.5 260 -40' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 170 140 L 245 65 Q 192.5 297.5 170 140 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='180' y='120' fill='white' font-size='14'>6</text><text x='200' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>O</text><text x='250' y='180' fill='white' font-size='14'>y = x²</text><text x='200' y='80' fill='white' font-size='14' transform='rotate(-50 200 80)'>y = x + 6</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Find intersection points<br><br>x² = x + 6<br>x² - x - 6 = 0<br>(x - 3)(x + 2) = 0<br>x = -2, 3<br><br>Step 2: Set up area integral<br><br>Area = ∫₋₂³ (x + 6 - x²) dx<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate<br><br>= [x²/2 + 6x - x³/3]₋₂³<br>= (9/2 + 18 - 9) - (2 - 12 + 8/3)<br>= 27/2 - (-22/3) = 81/6 + 44/6 = 125/6<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 125/6</strong>"},
  
  {"type": "math_show", "q": "19. Find the shaded area.", "c": "<div style='width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px; background: #1e1e1e; border-radius: 8px;'><svg viewBox='0 0 400 400' width='100%' height='100%' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><line x1='0' y1='200' x2='400' y2='200' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><line x1='200' y1='0' x2='200' y2='400' stroke='#FFFFFF' stroke-width='2'/><path d='M 150 70 Q 300 70 300 200' fill='none' stroke='#00EEFF' stroke-width='4'/><path d='M 200 200 L 200 130 Q 280 130 300 200 Z' fill='rgba(0,238,255,0.3)'/><text x='170' y='135' fill='white' font-size='14'>√2</text><text x='190' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>0</text><text x='295' y='215' fill='white' font-size='14'>2</text><text x='220' y='125' fill='white' font-size='14'>f(x) = 2 - x</text></svg></div><br><br><strong>အဖြေရှင်းလင်းချက်:</strong><br><br>Step 1: Set up the integral<br><br>Area = ∫₀² √(2 - x) dx<br><br>Step 2: Use substitution<br><br>Let u = 2 - x, then du = -dx<br>When x = 0, u = 2. When x = 2, u = 0<br><br>Area = ∫₂⁰ √u (-du) = ∫₀² u^(1/2) du<br><br>Step 3: Evaluate<br><br>= [2u^(3/2)/3]₀² = 2/3 (2)^(3/2) = 2/3 (2√2) = 4√2/3<br><br><strong>အဖြေ: 4√2/3</strong>"}
]
